The very top!
<%import>
  java.math.BigDecimal
</%import>

<%args>
  BigDecimal amount
  int x => 3
  int y => 7
</%args>

Here is a template. It has two arguments:

x, which is <% x %>,
and amount, which is <% amount %>.
%  for (int i = 0; i < y; ++i)
% {
i is <% i %>.
<%java> } </%java>

Some escaping stuff:

HTML Escaped: <% "&" %> <% ">" %> <% "<" %> <% "'" %> <% "\"" %>

XML escaped: <% "&"   |x  %> <% ">" |x%> <% "<"   |x %> <% "'" |x%> <% "\"" |x %>

URL escaped: <% "&"   |u  %> <% ">" |u%> <% "<"   |u %> <% "'" |u%> <% "\"" |u %>

Not escaped: <% "&"   |n  %> <% ">" |n%> <% "<"   |n %> <% "'" |n%> <% "\"" |n %>

This is a call: <& /foo/bar; a => 3 &>
So is this: <& baz/bop/boop; qwer => "asdf"; zxcvzx => foo.bar(6,"asdf") &>
